We should add the filenames in sorted-order to facilitate file rotation. eg: recovery/log_file recovery/log_file.1 and so on. Thus the caller does not _need_ to run multiple passes to get the directory, then act upon it. e.g. if recovery/log_file does not exist, there is no need to rotate the filenames on 'refresh' cycle.

